/**
 * @namespace Filters
 */

module.exports = {
  /**
   * Remove a token from the ditribution output if it contains a key `private` set to true
   *
   * @memberof Filters
   * 
   * @param {Object} token
   * @returns {Boolean} 
   */
  removePrivate: function(token) {
    return (token && token.private) ? false : true
  }
}
